gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 144, Nets 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeat the Nets, 144-122.  Giannis Antetokounmpo led the way with 32 points, 10 rebounds and eight assists for the Bucks, while Khris Middleton added 27 points and 10 assists in the victory.  Jalen Wilson led the Nets with 21 points and 10 rebounds in the losing effort.  The Bucks improve to 23-8 on the season, while the Nets fall to 15-16.
